very hour using a time-weighted average premium between the perpetual and mark prices. The hybrid sequencer processes funding payments off-chain before settling on Arbitrum, reducing gas costs while maintaining transparency. Cross-margin is enabled by default, allowing efficient capital utilization across positions. Funding payments are automatically settled in USDT with real-time balance updates through the off-chain sequencer."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
